    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead">Are you looking to start a career in communication and PR or do you already work in the sector and want professional development? This flexible PgCert in Strategic Communication and Public Relations course will enable you to develop your communications and public relations knowledge and skills without the commitment of full-time study, making it ideal for those with existing work commitments.</span></p>
<p>You will develop the specialist skills needed to communicate effectively across a range of media and digital platforms. It’s important to understand the bigger picture, and you will study within a framework that emphasises strategic thinking and a critical stance, enabling you to make an effective, ethical and responsible contribution to your organisation.</p>
<p>The course is delivered both full and part-time with start dates in September and January. </p>]]></Value>
